        pricing_overview: '<p>Repl AI adopts a straightforward SaaS subscription model. A basic "Free Trial" or highly limited tier is often utilized to demonstrate the terrifying speed of generation. Subsequent paid tiers (usually billed monthly) focus heavily on removing generation caps, unlocking access to smarter underlying LLM models (e.g., upgrading from GPT-3.5 to GPT-4 for more nuanced replies), and allowing the creation of infinite custom personas.</p>',
