        pricing_overview: '<p>Resemble AI utilizes a structure heavily focused on enterprise consumption. The "Basic" "Pay-as-you-go" tier allows smaller creators to pay strictly per second of generated audio. However, the true power of the platform is locked behind the "Pro" or "Enterprise" tiers, which require massive monthly recurring commitments to unlock unlimited custom voice creation, the proprietary deepfake watermarking algorithms, real-time gaming APIs, and mandatory legal consent verification.</p>',
