        pricing_overview: '<p>Retool operates a massive B2B Enterprise SaaS model based explicitly on "Seats." A Generous "Free" tier allows developers to build massive applications. However, to actually deploy those applications to teams securely, Retool charges a monthly fee per "Creator" (Engineer) and per "End User" (Support Rep clicking the buttons). Enterprise tiers are required for massive deployments, unlocking On-Premise hosting, White-labeling (removing the Retool logo), and complex Git version control.</p>',
