            { group: 'Advanced Audio Intelligence', items: ['Speaker Diarization (algorithmically separating John\'s voice from Sarah\'s voice)', 'Custom Vocabulary injection (forcing the AI to recognize a bizarre corporate acronym correctly)', 'Topic Extraction prioritizing key themes within the audio', 'Automated punctuation and capitalization casing models'] }
