            { title: 'Generative Data Enrichment', description: 'Users populate a column with a list of generic company URLs; utilizing the native OpenAI integration, they run a prompt down the entire column instructing the AI to "Visit this URL and write a 1-sentence summary of what they sell," enriching 500 rows instantly.' }
