        best_for: ['Modern Digital Marketing and Growth Agencies', 'Agile Operations Teams routing data across multiple SaaS tools', 'Startup Founders needing beautiful, live investor dashboards', 'Anyone who hates the agonizing process of exporting CSV files from 10 different platforms daily'],
