        pricing_overview: '<p>Rows utilizes a highly modern, incredibly generous Freemium strategy. The massive Free tier is universally acclaimed, allowing individuals absolute access to the grid, basic API integrations, and the foundational AI analyst to establish extreme user lock-in. Premium tiers ("Plus" and "Pro") scale primarily via computational bulk—unlocking massive automated data refresh rates, allowing API calls for tens of thousands of rows simultaneously, increasing AI limits, and adding sophisticated team permissions.</p>',
